column5: Hi all,  The name Is Colin. I've been visiting your site here and there and found it to be the best one to become a member. I love fishing and hunting. I hope to learn some new tricks and share mine. Its a pleasure and hope to see ya on the water.
Keep an eye on ^this^ guy eh.    Welcome.  Jump in.

Welcome, that was my favourite cartoon , JUST DON'T MOVE TO YELLOWKNIFE, you won't have any money left to buy lures or ice agers lol, welcome look forward to your postings, just my little rant about parking tickets and ice augers, I'll go to bed now.
I about spit my coffee out when I read that .. Quite fitting welcome aboard.
Pull up a chair and join right in.
straight jackets optional at this point....welcome aboard
Welcome to the board.  You'll have lottsa fun here!  "Nuthouse" probably!
Welcome - love the Icon, definitely the best of the loony tune dudes.  Be sure to leave the martians in a jar at home when you hit the river.
Welcome to the empty wallet club
Don't forget your full metal one as well.LOL  Welcome
Old member saying Hi and welcome to the board.
